body_html:
You get different error for different runs because: there are many errors, not only one. This is very like invoking gmake with "-j".

Please add " --verbose_failures" to your build command, so we can see more logs.

BTW, the code under r1.3 branch is not compilable right now, because of the sha256sum issue.
